'''西蒙·辛格'''（{{lang-en|Simon Singh}}，{{bd|1964年|9月19日|}}），[[印度裔英國人|印度裔]]，是一位[[英国|英国]][[大众科学|科普]]作家和理论物理学家。

==生平==
本科毕业于[[伦敦帝国学院|伦敦帝国学院]]，博士毕业于[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]<ref>{{cite web   | title = Faculty and Staff : MIT Grad Program in Science Writing   | url = http://sciwrite.mit.edu/faculty   | accessdate = 2014-03-14   | archive-date = 2019-04-20   | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190420210813/http://sciwrite.mit.edu/faculty   | dead-url = no   }}</ref>，主要作品有《[[费马大定理|费马大定理]]：{{le|费马大定理：一个困惑了世间智者358年的谜|Fermat's Last Theorem (book)|一个困惑了世间智者358年的谜}}》（''Fermat's Enigma: The Epic Quest to Solve the World's Greatest Mathematical Problem''，1997）<ref name="fermatslast">{{cite book | last=Singh | first= Simon | title=Fermat's Last Theorem | url=https://archive.org/details/fermatslasttheor0000unse | publisher=Fourth Estate | year=1997 | isbn=1-85702-669-1}}</ref><ref name="fermatsenigma">{{cite book | last=Singh | first= Simon | title=Fermat's Enigma: The Epic Quest to Solve the World's Greatest Mathematical Problem | title-link= Fermat's Enigma | publisher=Anchor | year=1998 | isbn=0-385-49362-2}}</ref>、《{{link-en|大爆炸简史|Big Bang (book)}}》（''Big Bang: The most important scientific discovery of all time and why you need to know about it''，2004）<ref name="bigbang">{{cite book | last=Singh | first= Simon | title=Big Bang: The Origin of the Universe | title-link= Big Bang (book) | publisher=Fourth Estate | year=2005 | isbn=0-00-716220-0}}</ref>等。

